WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.360
Well, good evening, family.

00:00:02.360 --> 00:00:05.177
Thank you for joining us again today.

00:00:07.560 --> 00:00:18.240
We're going to go over some things some people have had questions concerning our ministry and why we're named what we're named and all things like that.

00:00:18.240 --> 00:00:22.147
So, we want to clear some things up because we've had some emails.

00:00:22.147 --> 00:00:24.160
Some are not so nice.

00:00:24.160 --> 00:00:36.480
People are pretty upset about things being, you know, sister clipboards or whatever you want to call them because they don't understand.

00:00:36.480 --> 00:00:40.240
But Diana wants to explain the foundation part of our name.

00:00:40.240 --> 00:00:43.655
We are not a foundation, for sure.

00:00:43.873 --> 00:00:47.354
I want you to know that we are not a foundation.

00:00:58.457 --> 00:01:04.320
We picked the name because prayer is a foundation, but we're an online church, and so the Prayer Changes Things Foundation is an online church if you see that in the description that we put in there.

00:01:17.467 --> 00:01:17.644
We have weekly online services, and so under US federal law, churches are automatically recognized as tax-exempt under section 501(c)(3) of the IRS and are not required to apply for formal recognition.

00:01:21.040 --> 00:01:24.880
So, we have an EIN and all of that, but we don't have to do what some of the more...

00:01:24.880 --> 00:01:27.973
like Joseph Z's ministry has a board and all.

00:01:27.973 --> 00:01:39.107
There are more requirements and stuff that they all do, but churches are also specifically exempt from the Form 990 filing requirement under the Internal Revenue Code 6033A 3 AI.

00:01:46.080 --> 00:01:50.560
So, everything we've done—I want to say this because people want to know because it's tax season—everything we have done, we have gone through lawyers.

00:01:51.280 --> 00:01:57.234
We have gone through people that have set it up that have been professional.

00:01:57.234 --> 00:02:01.851
My wife has a Master's degree in accounting.

00:02:08.280 --> 00:02:10.740
So, a lot of times you say, 'Well, Brandon, how come Diana is not on the broadcast today?

00:02:10.740 --> 00:02:20.429
' I want to tell you this—and we don't tell our business to everybody about everything—but she has a Master's degree in accounting and in business.

00:02:20.429 --> 00:02:23.016
She graduated top of her class.

00:02:35.620 --> 00:02:35.930
I was proud of her.

00:02:35.930 --> 00:02:37.796
I wanted to show her awards.

00:02:37.796 --> 00:02:41.577
She got her Summa Cum Laude awards.

00:02:41.577 --> 00:02:44.640
She got all her awards from ORU.

00:02:44.640 --> 00:02:47.900
She got her degree in accounting.

00:02:47.900 --> 00:02:56.575
She is very educated, and she graduated top of her class as she got awards and everything.

00:02:56.575 --> 00:03:04.080
So, I want you to know a lot of times it's not that she is trying to avoid prayer with everybody.

00:03:04.080 --> 00:03:07.233
Why is Diana not here?

00:03:07.233 --> 00:03:10.898
How come she doesn't want to be a part?

00:03:10.898 --> 00:03:12.204
She's working a full-time job.

00:03:12.204 --> 00:03:12.773
She's very educated.

00:03:12.773 --> 00:03:14.910
She's been working at this for years.

00:03:24.125 --> 00:03:27.672
And I didn't want her to give up her career of what she was doing, selling on eBay and Poshmark and doing the things that she has done for this.

00:03:27.672 --> 00:03:29.624
We don't depend on the ministry for finances.

00:03:29.624 --> 00:03:31.220
My wife works full-time.

00:03:45.200 --> 00:03:45.400
I do YouTube.

00:03:54.955 --> 00:03:55.360
We have a ministry property.

00:03:56.440 --> 00:03:59.354
The ministry has purchased a ministry property.

00:04:08.312 --> 00:04:09.384
That's different.

00:04:09.384 --> 00:04:11.480
I'm going to be straight up front with you.

00:04:11.480 --> 00:04:12.380
That is totally different.

00:04:12.380 --> 00:04:15.800
We did buy a ministry property.

00:04:15.800 --> 00:04:17.690
So, it's not shocking and all.

00:04:17.690 --> 00:04:22.994
When you have as much coming through, when you have this many people coming through, money flows through here.

00:04:22.994 --> 00:04:26.700
And I'm going to tell you this: I have never taken a vow of poverty.

00:04:26.700 --> 00:04:28.524
I'm not afraid of what I have.

00:04:28.524 --> 00:04:30.053
I'm not ashamed of what I have.

00:04:30.053 --> 00:04:43.080
I'm going to tell you this: I was instructed by the FBI to get a safe haven for me and my family because I've had threats on my life all the time on a consistent basis.

00:04:43.080 --> 00:04:49.660
Where we were at our old house, we have people showing up knocking on our door.

00:04:49.660 --> 00:05:01.833
And I'm going to tell you this: when you have an audience like we do and the people that hate us as much as they do, I just want to tell you, I have to protect my family.

00:05:01.833 --> 00:05:03.400
Now, we have attorneys.

00:05:03.400 --> 00:05:05.160
We've had to hire full-time security.

00:05:05.160 --> 00:05:22.827
We're having to look into full-time security to have to watch over me because of the incidents, but because of what I've been told by the sheriff's department, local law enforcement, and the FBI, I must provide protection for my family because of these threats, and they tell me they're legitimate.

00:05:22.827 --> 00:05:26.296
Now, I try to be as transparent as I can.

00:05:26.296 --> 00:05:32.680
I try not to tell where my address is and things like that because I have people that have tried to physically hurt me.

00:05:32.680 --> 00:05:39.800
So, if you think, 'Well, Brandon, you're secretive,' you don't understand Charlie Kirk was real.

00:05:39.800 --> 00:05:41.020
Do you understand that?

00:05:41.020 --> 00:05:48.960
So, when I feel a need and I feel it in my spirit to leave and go stay in a hotel that night, it's because the Lord's warning me to.

00:05:48.960 --> 00:06:03.058
I've had crazy people stay at IHOP for seven days demanding me to give them a word, and they thought they had a word, and they shaved their heads to look just like me and drive around the same place as I have.

00:06:03.058 --> 00:06:05.320
I have nuts follow us.

00:06:05.320 --> 00:06:08.640
And I'm just being quite frank; I don't ever talk about it.

00:06:08.640 --> 00:06:14.246
We don't talk about all this stuff, but there's a lot of emails and there's been a lot of hate lately about what I do with my life.

00:06:14.246 --> 00:06:19.760
And I don't tell you everything because I'm trying to keep my family safe, okay?

00:06:19.760 --> 00:06:22.160
There are a lot of people that hate me.

00:06:22.160 --> 00:06:22.540
Yes.

00:06:22.540 --> 00:06:30.600
And you have no idea what happens behind closed doors and the conversations that I have strictly with...

00:06:30.600 --> 00:06:32.280
Should I say that?

00:06:32.280 --> 00:06:34.080
No.

00:06:34.080 --> 00:06:40.680
Yeah, some of the people that I contact are in direct contact with the President of the United States of America.

00:06:40.680 --> 00:06:46.480
The messages that I deliver are received by the White House.

00:06:47.107 --> 00:06:54.520
I've told you I have been invited to the White House more than once, and I have turned it down every single time.

00:06:54.952 --> 00:06:59.750
I'm trying to tell you all, I don't try to come on here and be all haughty and say, 'Look at me.

00:06:59.750 --> 00:07:00.967
' It's not about Brandon.

00:07:00.967 --> 00:07:10.240
But people look at accuracy, and whenever they see things that you don't know that they know and they say, 'How did you find this out?

00:07:10.240 --> 00:07:12.240
' So they say, 'How did you know this?

00:07:12.240 --> 00:07:13.800
' I've been asked that many times.

00:07:13.800 --> 00:07:15.074
'How did you know this?

00:07:15.074 --> 00:07:16.589
Do you have somebody on the inside?

00:07:16.589 --> 00:07:18.680
' I said, 'No, it's all Jesus.

00:07:18.680 --> 00:07:21.919
' And I have to explain to law enforcement quite often.

00:07:21.919 --> 00:07:25.480
I want you to know I do this all for Him.

00:07:25.480 --> 00:07:30.500
I told you as soon as He tells me to turn this channel off, I'll ride away in the sunset.

00:07:31.480 --> 00:07:38.720
There's nothing you can give me, honest to God, that my wife hasn't worked eight years for a degree and is very good at it.

00:07:40.160 --> 00:07:44.996
The same with me; I could do other things to help out around the house.

00:07:44.996 --> 00:07:46.760
I raised dogs.

00:07:46.760 --> 00:07:48.680
I raised all these things.

00:07:48.680 --> 00:07:50.725
We did this because the Lord asked us to do it.

00:07:50.725 --> 00:07:51.050
Yes.

00:07:51.050 --> 00:07:52.675
And it hasn't been easy.

00:07:52.675 --> 00:07:53.789
It hasn't been easy.

00:07:53.789 --> 00:07:55.940
And there's people that say I'm a false prophet.

00:07:55.940 --> 00:07:56.851
You say I'm fake.

00:07:56.851 --> 00:07:57.857
I'm all these things.

00:07:57.857 --> 00:07:58.590
That's on you.

00:07:58.590 --> 00:08:00.200
I don't care what you really think.

00:08:00.200 --> 00:08:08.069
Whenever the rubber meets the road and you see, and I'm standing before my King, I'll be held accountable by Him.

00:08:08.069 --> 00:08:13.260
If I've led anybody astray by any words I give, I take it very seriously.

00:08:13.260 --> 00:08:18.400
This is a very heavy responsibility.

00:08:18.400 --> 00:08:26.320
Nobody will understand the pressure that I'm under on a 99% basis and crying myself to sleep because of the pressure.

00:08:26.320 --> 00:08:28.270
I want you to understand.

00:08:28.270 --> 00:08:30.720
We come back on here with a smile on our face.

00:08:31.680 --> 00:08:33.120
I'm always transparent.

00:08:33.120 --> 00:08:39.520
I don't tell you where I live on purpose because there are crazy people trying to hurt me.

00:08:39.520 --> 00:08:40.274
Do you understand?

00:08:40.274 --> 00:08:42.999
Now, people want to try to expose me and say, 'Hey, this is where he's at.

00:08:42.999 --> 00:08:43.667
This is where he's at.

00:08:43.667 --> 00:08:44.622
' I have to buy another house.

00:08:44.622 --> 00:08:45.564
I have to do this.

00:08:45.564 --> 00:08:46.986
I have to get away.

00:08:46.986 --> 00:08:47.555
Hey, listen.

00:08:47.555 --> 00:08:48.079
I have...

00:08:48.079 --> 00:08:49.520
the Lord has blessed my wife.

00:08:49.520 --> 00:08:51.040
We're blessed.

00:08:51.040 --> 00:08:53.933
So, like I said, I'm not trying to take anything from you all.

00:08:54.800 --> 00:08:56.480
If you want to bless my family, that's on you.

00:08:58.080 --> 00:08:59.200
That's on you.

00:08:59.973 --> 00:09:05.900
But like I said, the Lord said go on YouTube and ask them for nothing.

00:09:05.900 --> 00:09:07.280
Nothing.

00:09:07.280 --> 00:09:07.880
And over the...

00:09:08.280 --> 00:09:13.140
it's like one of the things I want to say this.

00:09:14.320 --> 00:09:23.520
When XRP was at 12 cents—and I'll say this, this is the only thing—I was buying.

00:09:23.880 --> 00:09:29.480
He tells me when to buy and he tells me when to sell.

00:09:29.480 --> 00:09:33.009
He tells me when silver's going up.

00:09:33.009 --> 00:09:35.000
He tells me when it crashes.

00:09:36.280 --> 00:09:40.829
I hear him very well, but I don't brag and I don't try to flex.

00:09:40.829 --> 00:09:48.200
People see it around the church and people get mad and they get jealous.

00:09:48.200 --> 00:09:52.169
Everything that I'm telling you is the truth, but I'm transparent about it.

00:09:52.169 --> 00:09:53.004
We're very transparent.

00:09:54.604 --> 00:09:54.796
I have nothing to hide from you.

00:10:00.253 --> 00:10:03.217
I have nothing to gain from you.

00:10:06.640 --> 00:10:08.600
I do these videos and I do all this for the glory of God.

00:10:08.600 --> 00:10:13.747
So, I wanted to make that very clear tonight.

00:10:13.747 --> 00:10:20.530
There's people that are very angry and I've gotten the emails and I say, 'Hey, man.

00:10:20.530 --> 00:10:22.840
We never asked you for a dime.

00:10:22.840 --> 00:10:25.400
I've never tried to solicit you.

00:10:31.154 --> 00:10:31.526
I don't sell books.

00:10:31.526 --> 00:10:35.240
I don't try to sell books.

00:10:35.240 --> 00:10:46.760
' I have been offered to put ads—like to make an ad on live—$100,000 a month to do ads and do things for this one company.

00:10:52.560 --> 00:10:52.840
And I told them no.

00:10:52.840 --> 00:10:54.240
The Lord said no.

00:10:54.240 --> 00:11:04.680
All I had to do was just do a little segment and put it on all my channels throughout all the world.

00:11:14.840 --> 00:11:15.200
I have seven channels—eight now.

00:11:34.142 --> 00:11:34.458
Put them on all those channels at the beginning for just a two-minute segment and they give me $100,000 a month.

00:11:34.458 --> 00:11:36.695
My flesh wanted to take that money.

00:11:50.623 --> 00:11:50.869
I'm not going to lie to you.

00:11:50.869 --> 00:11:53.543
I was like, 'That's over a million dollars a year.

00:11:53.543 --> 00:11:56.600
Of course, we'll do it.

00:11:56.600 --> 00:12:02.580
' And Diana goes, 'You took a vow to God.

00:12:03.420 --> 00:12:05.297
You will not take that money.

00:12:05.297 --> 00:12:08.096
We will not take that money.

00:12:08.096 --> 00:12:24.800
' Then I had a businessman fly in from Japan who told me he would let me fly around in his private jet for free and give me hundreds of thousands of dollars to be his friend and give him financial advice and things.

00:12:29.578 --> 00:12:29.796
I do not give financial advice to anyone.

00:12:33.176 --> 00:12:33.432
We fear God more than people realize.

00:12:33.432 --> 00:12:34.712
They don't know us.

00:12:47.129 --> 00:12:47.360
It is everything.

00:12:54.693 --> 00:12:55.040
This life goes away.

00:12:55.040 --> 00:13:02.345
But when we get to heaven, a lot of people put so much into what they feel like they can do on earth.

00:13:19.987 --> 00:13:20.253
But it's really about what we can do.

00:13:20.253 --> 00:13:25.140
What we are doing now is affecting our eternity for the kingdom.

00:13:25.140 --> 00:13:31.876
And I take it very seriously, very, very seriously, to work for the Lord, to do what we're doing.

00:13:39.400 --> 00:13:39.720
And I'm behind the scenes just doing what I've done for years, just doing my eBay and Poshmark.

00:13:39.720 --> 00:13:43.355
Done this for a long time—at least a decade.

00:13:43.355 --> 00:13:44.455
Over a decade.

00:13:44.455 --> 00:13:47.693
So, and taxes, things that you can do.

00:13:50.120 --> 00:13:53.051
You do understand when you have a master's degree, why you don't let it die.

00:13:53.051 --> 00:13:53.600
She worked.

00:13:53.600 --> 00:13:56.969
She went to school for forever—over eight years.

00:14:09.320 --> 00:14:09.640
And I told her, I said, 'I'm not asking you to give up your education to do this.

00:14:09.640 --> 00:14:12.349
If God calls you to come beside me, that's fine, baby.

00:14:12.349 --> 00:14:12.811
I understand.

00:14:12.811 --> 00:14:18.120
We don't want what we've done for years that has provided for us to die.

00:14:18.120 --> 00:14:21.046
' So, I want to make that clear.

00:14:21.046 --> 00:14:24.989
She homeschools and does the things that we do.

00:14:29.080 --> 00:14:29.267
It's a lot.

00:14:30.760 --> 00:14:31.720
But Diana is a full-time working person plus homeschools.

00:14:32.200 --> 00:14:41.977
And then she sends out thank you letters to the people that have blessed us and says, 'Listen, she writes every single one of them out by hand.

00:14:41.977 --> 00:14:49.940
' She writes it and she does things and she goes, 'Brandon, I feel like they deserve a thank you.

00:14:49.940 --> 00:14:53.860
' I said, 'Diana, you don't have time for this.

00:14:53.860 --> 00:14:56.733
People—I just think y'all are so kind.

00:14:56.733 --> 00:15:04.262
There's so many people that just love us and just love what we're doing for God.

00:15:04.262 --> 00:15:12.326
' And it's all many hands on deck as we're doing this final push, as he's coming so soon.

00:15:12.326 --> 00:15:19.954
And there's such an urgency of the hour.

00:15:20.440 --> 00:15:32.340
I know people say, 'Well, they've been saying he's going to come back for so long,' but he is coming so soon.

00:15:40.293 --> 00:15:44.000
And I take it very seriously that I'll take any load I can off of him so that he can keep going, so we can keep going for the Lord.

00:15:44.000 --> 00:15:46.669
We do it all for the Lord.

00:15:46.669 --> 00:15:48.533
I'd give everything away.

00:15:48.533 --> 00:15:50.960
It doesn't matter.

00:15:50.960 --> 00:15:52.335
Nothing matters to me.

00:15:52.335 --> 00:16:07.160
It's just keeping on course and finishing this race and doing it with everything we have so that we can stand before our king and go, 'We did our best we could.

00:16:13.056 --> 00:16:13.308
I tried my best,' you know?

00:16:17.253 --> 00:16:24.040
And I can see, you know, we believe every day Megan's going to get healed.

00:16:35.600 --> 00:16:35.895
But one day, I know for sure there's going to be a day—if it's not here, it's there.

00:16:35.895 --> 00:16:48.103
So now I have to hire full-time security that's going to cost me over $100,000 a year because I have idiots that want to know where I live.

00:16:51.920 --> 00:16:52.505
And I said, 'Well, I knew it was coming.

00:16:52.505 --> 00:16:55.680
The Lord told me: I'm going to make you a household name.

00:16:55.680 --> 00:17:05.890
' He said, 'You're going to be known all around the world and it's happening.

00:17:05.890 --> 00:17:15.864
' And he said, 'And in doing so, like Oral Roberts had to have security 24/7 and other ministries, you will have to also.

00:17:15.864 --> 00:17:18.528
' So I've already looked into it today.

00:17:18.528 --> 00:17:30.164
I'm telling you, it's going to cost me a ton of money, but it is what it is, and it's part of the price of doing what God's called me to do.

00:17:40.080 --> 00:17:40.435
So, I'll have an armed guard continually at my home.

00:17:40.435 --> 00:17:42.920
That sucks, but it is what it is.

00:17:42.920 --> 00:17:52.080
And he'll travel with me to services so maybe I'll start going to other people's ministries because I'll have security now.

00:17:52.080 --> 00:18:03.912
You know, I thought I could start taking preaching engagements and not have to worry if the church has security anymore because I'll have somebody—ex-military is what I'm looking into.

00:18:05.312 --> 00:18:10.462
And having this ex-military 24/7, seven days a week around me and my wife and my kids because of the threats I get.

00:18:20.440 --> 00:18:20.771
So, I appreciate your prayers.

00:18:21.103 --> 00:18:22.097
I truly do.

00:18:24.530 --> 00:18:25.380
It has been very hard.

00:18:25.380 --> 00:18:40.303
I never knew some of the things that I would say would bring up so much hatred by so many different groups of people that are not playing around when it comes to your life.

00:18:45.600 --> 00:18:58.110
I didn't realize, you know, when you see politicians get their lives threatened and you see John Hagee in the past—the guy missed him six times, shooting at him and all the things.

00:19:09.968 --> 00:19:10.216
This stuff's real.

00:19:10.216 --> 00:19:11.407
Charlie Kirk's real.

00:19:23.840 --> 00:19:34.040
And there comes a point in time where the world doesn't understand the value of life and just having a man just doing what he's called to do, praying online with thousands and hundreds of thousands every time I do this—hundreds of thousands of people worldwide.

00:19:41.560 --> 00:19:41.720
This is so much more than I ever dreamed: the pressure and the responsibility of it.

00:19:41.720 --> 00:19:50.653
Making sure you're not flaky and making sure you're accurate so that you represent him well.

00:19:58.560 --> 00:19:58.880
And the week that we've had and the last two weeks we've had, it has been really rough.

00:19:58.880 --> 00:20:07.260
But I give all glory and honor because he said you'll be persecuted for the word's sake.

00:20:07.260 --> 00:20:08.686
And then he warned me.

00:20:08.686 --> 00:20:15.324
He said, 'The one person who's persecuting you, Brandon, will be dead within 16 months.

00:20:15.324 --> 00:20:17.760
' And he warned me about it.

00:20:17.760 --> 00:20:22.457
And I said, 'Lord, spare their life.

00:20:22.457 --> 00:20:24.520
Protect them.

00:20:24.520 --> 00:20:26.680
Protect them.

00:20:26.680 --> 00:20:39.840
' He said they've opened a door and because of this door, they're going to be gone in 16 months.

00:20:42.920 --> 00:20:45.775
And I don't know what that means, but I've been interceding for them all day long.

00:20:45.775 --> 00:20:50.440
Praying for these people, praying for the people who persecute.

00:20:50.440 --> 00:20:54.610
Like I said, we love you.

00:20:54.610 --> 00:20:55.990
We forgive people.

00:20:55.990 --> 00:21:00.469
We're not holding a grudge towards anyone.

00:21:00.469 --> 00:21:05.320
We have a child with special needs.

00:21:05.320 --> 00:21:15.320
We do all these things and Diana, like I said, works her tail end off.

00:21:15.320 --> 00:21:26.180
I'm thankful for all the people who like, subscribe, click the notification bell, and I'm thankful for YouTube.

00:21:26.180 --> 00:21:36.840
They pay me well for all the ads and it's been, like I said, I do that and I go, 'Hey, man, Lord, you've taken care of things.

00:21:36.840 --> 00:21:40.456
' It is what it is.

00:21:40.456 --> 00:21:43.072
I have seven channels.

00:21:43.072 --> 00:21:47.507
Each one gets tens of thousands of views.

00:21:47.507 --> 00:21:52.840
It's all because he's blessed it.

00:21:52.840 --> 00:21:58.400
And when we got monetized on X, I was shocked.

00:21:58.400 --> 00:22:09.943
And when it's time for us to go off YouTube, if he ever tells us to, when I was monetized on Facebook and X, I was shocked.

